body:
Hi everyone, I created a double glazed window, with a 8mm low-e glass, 12mm air gap, and a 8mm tempered clear glass on the inside in Window 7.3. I then imported the bdsf into honeybee and I'm getting the following readme message: void BSDF Glazing
6 0.000 C:/Users/Public/LBNL/WINDOW7.3/BSDFs/Glazing.xml 0.000 0.000 1.000 .
0
0


I'm not saying this is an error but I am obviously worried about the values the component is reporting.
Any ideas? Thanks in advance. Theodore.
